    • Event

      public Event(String eventId, String event_name, String event_description, int event_price, int event_max_entrants, Date registration_open, Date registration_close, String facilityId, String event_location, boolean geolocation_requirement, String event_image_path)
      Constructor for initializing an Event instance with essential details.
      Parameters:
      eventId - Unique identifier for the event.
      event_name - Name of the event.
      event_description - Description of the event.
      event_price - Cost to enter the event.
      event_max_entrants - Maximum number of entrants.
      registration_open - Date when registration opens.
      registration_close - Date when registration closes.
      facilityId - ID of the facility where the event is held.
      event_location - Location of the event (facility location).
      geolocation_requirement - Whether geolocation is required for the event.
      event_image_path - Path to the facility's image.
